100 Books by August Derleth is bibliography of books by American author August Derleth . It was released in 1962 by Arkham House in an edition of 1,225 copies . Approxiamtely 200 copies were bound in boards for libraries . Verona , WI : E.V.A. , 1974 . Jaffery , Sheldon ( 1989 ) . The Arkham House Companion . Mercer Island , WA : Starmont House , Inc. , 63 . Chalker , Jack L . ; Mark Owings ( 1998 ) . The Science - Fantasy Publishers : A Bibliographic History , 1923 - 1998 . Westminster , MD and Baltimore : Mirage Press , Ltd. , 40 . Joshi , S.T. ( 1999 ) . Sixty Years of Arkham House : A History and Bibliography . Sauk City , WI : Arkham House , 77 - 78 . Nielsen , Leon ( 2004 ) . Arkham House Books : A Collector 's Guide . Jefferson , NC and London : McFarland & Company , Inc. , 86 . 